OL,5, A Tory MP is standing by comments he   
OL,6, made that firefighters earning #32,000 
OL,7, a year who use food banks should "learn
OL,8, how to budget".                        
OL,10,FBrendan Clarke-Smith tweeted that the  
OL,11,Fidea of people on this money using a   
OL,12,Ffood bank was the most "ridiculous"    
OL,13,Fthing he had heard.                    
OL,15,F"If true", he added, they should learn 
OL,16,F"how to budget and prioritise".        
OL,18,FHis remarks sparked a row, with many   
OL,19,Fpeople highlighting the soaring costs  
OL,20,Fof energy, food, fuel and rent.        
